Package: apch
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Partial Conjunction Hypotheses Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Yuxin", "Li", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
  person("Zicheng", "Lu", role = "aut"),
  person("Xiaolei", "Lin", role = "aut")
 )
Description: Two-layer hierarchical framework for multi-trait (or multi-feature)
  association analysis with adaptive shrinkage at the feature level and
  block-diagonal EM at the configuration level. Supports correlated features,
  grid distillation, and parallel execution.
